<section class="page-title parallax parallax6">
  <div class="title-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <div class="box-title color-black">
            <h1>동국대 멋쟁이 사자처럼</h1>
            <h2>갤러리</h2>
